{
  "chapter": 39,
  "chapter_summary": "傅红雪按挑衅字条来到节妇坊，遇见自称参与梅花庵血案的郭威。郭威逼他将郭家满门杀尽，连幼童也被仇恨推向刀锋；暗中飞刀杀童后，傅红雪被诬为懦夫，为维护白天羽名声而陷入血战。重伤醒来后，翠浓前来照顾他，两人故作冷淡又互相刺痛。翠浓谎称已嫁王大洪，傅红雪强忍痛苦祝福并盘问王大洪，终于识破此人只是临时冒充。翠浓坦白自己只是怕被赶走，仍深爱傅红雪；傅红雪也承认非她不可，两人相拥许诺永不分离。章末王大洪忽然亮出疑似淬毒短剑，温情转为危机。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "匿名留书者",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "傅红雪，你若有种，就到节妇坊来吧。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪内心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们等的究竟是一个什么样的人？这个人会不会来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_wei",
      "speaker_name": "郭威",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我姓郭，叫做郭威！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_wei",
      "speaker_name": "郭威",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你就是白天羽的后人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_guo_wei",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_wei",
      "speaker_name": "郭威",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_guo_wei",
      "text": "你找我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_wei",
      "speaker_name": "郭威",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我有件事要告诉你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_guo_wei",
      "text": "我本就是来听的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_wei",
      "speaker_name": "郭威",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我也是那天晚上在梅花庵外杀害你父亲的人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_wei",
      "speaker_name": "郭威",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我一直在等着他的后人来复仇，已等了十九年！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_guo_wei",
      "text": "我已来了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_wei",
      "speaker_name": "郭威",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我杀了姓白的一家人，你若要复仇，就该把姓郭的一家人也全都杀尽杀绝！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_wei",
      "speaker_name": "郭威",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "现在我们一家人已全都在这里等着你，你若让一个人活着，就不配做白天羽的儿子。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_wei",
      "speaker_name": "郭威",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你还等什么？为什么还不过来动手？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jia_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "郭家小孩",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你要杀我爷爷，我也要杀你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_wei",
      "speaker_name": "郭威",
      "listener": "char_guo_jia_xiao_hai",
      "text": "好，好孩子，不愧是姓郭的！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪内心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你杀了我父亲，所以我要复仇！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jia_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "郭家小孩内心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要杀我爷爷，所以我也要杀你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_wei",
      "speaker_name": "郭威",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你既然连这孩子都能杀，为什么还不拔你的刀？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_guo_wei",
      "text": "这孩子不是我杀的！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_wei",
      "speaker_name": "郭威",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "杀了人还不敢承认？想不到白天羽的儿子竟是个说谎的懦夫。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪内心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白天羽的头颅，莫非也是被这样砍下来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪内心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我死活都没有关系，但我却绝不能让别人认为白天羽的儿子是个说谎的懦夫！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪内心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我绝不能让他死了后还受人侮辱！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪记忆中的声音",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "让你的仇人全都死尽死绝，否则你也不要回来见我！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁观者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这柄刀本不属于人间，这是一柄来自地狱中的魔刀！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "郭家人",
      "listener": "char_guo_wei",
      "text": "退下去！全都退下去！留下一条命，以后再复仇！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你醒了！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你应该再多睡一会儿的，我已叫人替你熬了粥。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "滚！滚出去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我不滚，也不出去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "是谁叫你来的？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "是我自己来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "你为什么要来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "因为我知道你病了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "我的事跟你完全没有关系，也用不着你管。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你的事跟我有关系，我一定要管的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "但我现在已不认得你，我根本就不认得你！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你认得我的，我也认得你。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "以前那些事，无论是你对不起我，还是我对不起你，我们都可以忘记，但我们总算还是朋友，你病了，我当然要来照顾你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我说过，你应该多休息休息，等粥好了，我再叫你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓内心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既然能将我当做朋友，我为什么还要去追寻往昔那种感情？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓内心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既然能这样冷静，我为什么还要让你看见我的痛苦？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪内心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一定要冷静，一定要让她相信，我也完全忘记了过去的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "谢谢你，要你来照顾我，实在不敢当。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "这也没什么，你也不必客气。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "但你总是客人，我应该招待你的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "大家既然都是老朋友了，你为什么还一定要这么客气？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "我心里总是过意不去。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "无论如何，我还是不应该这样子麻烦你的。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我说过没关系，反正我丈夫也知道我在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "你丈夫？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "对了，我竟忘了告诉你，我已经嫁了人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "恭喜你。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "恭喜你。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "恭喜你。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "每个女人——不论是怎么样的女人，迟早都要找个归宿，迟早都要嫁人的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你既然不要我，我只好嫁给别人了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "你的丈夫是不是也来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "他就在外面？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "那么你就应该出去陪他，为什么还要留在这里？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我说过，我要照顾你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "我并不想要你照顾，也不想让别人误会……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你用不着担心这些事，所有的事他全都知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "他知道什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他知道你这个人，也知道我们过去的感情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "我们……我们之间其实并没有什么感情。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "不管怎么样，反正我已将以前那些事全都告诉了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "所以你就更不该到这里来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我到这里来找你，也已告诉了他，他也同意让我来照顾你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "看来他倒是个很开通的人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他的确是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "但我却并不是，我一点也不开通。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你若真的怕别人误会，我可以叫他进来一起陪你。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "text": "喂，你进来，我替你介绍一个朋友。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "text": "喂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他就是我的丈夫，他姓王，叫王大洪。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "text": "这位就是我跟你说起过的傅红雪，傅公子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "speaker_name": "王大洪",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "傅公子的大名，在下已久仰了。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "恭喜你，恭喜你们。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他是个老实人，一向很少跟别人来往，所以连话都不会说。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "不说话很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他也不会武功。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "不会武功很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他是个生意人，作的是个绸缎生意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "作生意很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他的确是个很好的人，至少他……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "至少他不会抛下我一个人溜走。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "speaker_name": "王大洪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "你们在这里多聊聊，我……我还是到外面去的好。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "text": "你请坐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "speaker_name": "王大洪",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "text": "人家叫你坐，你为什么还不坐下去？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "text": "你们成亲已经有多久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "speaker_name": "王大洪",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "已经有……有……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "已经快十天了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 706,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "speaker_name": "王大洪",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "不错，已经快十天了，到今天才九天。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 708
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "text": "你们是早就认得的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 710
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "speaker_name": "王大洪",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "不是……是……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "text": "你不是作绸缎生意的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_hong",
      "speaker_name": "王大洪",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我……我……我……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 722,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "他也不是你的丈夫。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "这个人究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "你也不知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 748,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他……他只不过是店里的伙计临时替我找来的，我根本不认得他。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 752
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "你找他来，为的就是要他冒充你的丈夫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 754,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "你为什么要这样做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 758
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "因为我想来看你，想来陪着你，照顾你，又怕你赶我走，因为我不愿让你觉得我是在死缠着你，不愿你觉得我是个下贱的女人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 760,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "其实我心里始终只有你，就算你不要我了，我也不会嫁给别人的，我自从跟你在一起后，就再也没有把别的男人看在眼里。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 774,
      "line_end": 776
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "谁说我不要你，谁说的？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 778
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你真的还要我？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "我当然要你，不管你是个怎么样的女人，我都要你，除了你之外，我再也不要别的女人了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 784
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "只要你真的要我，从今之后，我再也不会走了，再也不会离开你。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 792,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "我也永远不会离开你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 796
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "永远？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 798,
      "line_end": 798
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "永远！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 800
    }
  ],
